Usage: set_clock_gating_check [-help] [<object_list>] [-fall]
                              [-hold <hold_value>] [-rise]
                              [-setup <setup_value>] [-high  | -low ]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>             # List of clocks, intances or pins (string, optional)
-fall                     # Applies the value to the falling signals
                          # (bool, optional)
-high                     # Sets non-controlling value of clock as high
                          # (bool, optional)
-hold <hold_value>        # Hold value (float, optional)
-low                      # Sets non-controlling value of clock as low
                          # (bool, optional)
-rise                     # Applies the value to the rising signals
                          # (bool, optional)
-setup <setup_value>      # Setup value (float, optional)